==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*μάχαιρα / machaira / makh'-ahee-rah
Probably feminine of a presumed derivative of [[μάχη]]; a knife, that is, dirk; figuratively war, judicial punishment: 

=== Noun ===
'''μάχαιρα'''
# [[sword]].

